title: Ecs_control_24h_rep1
characteristics_ch1: cell type: exosomes from endothelial cells
treatment_protocol_ch1: The supernatants of ECs were centrifuged at 300 × g for 10 min to remove cell components and collected the supernatants. Then the supernatants were further centrifuged at 2000 × g for 10 min and again centrifuged at 10,000 g for 60 min. After that, the supernatants were centrifuged with ultracentrifuge (Beckman, Optima XPN-100) at 110,000g × g for 70 min at 4 °C. The exosomes pellets were then washed with pre-cooling PBS followed by a second ultracentrifugation at 110,000× g for 70 min to precipitate the exosomes. Then the supernatants were discarded and the exosomes pellet was re-suspended in an appropriate amount of pre-cooling PBS and store at -80 °C for further study.
growth_protocol_ch1: ECs monoculture subjected to low shear stress together with or without melatonin treatment.
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was labeled and purified by FlashTag™ Biotin HSR RNA Labeling Kit (P/N 901911, Affymetrix) according to the manufacturer’s instructions to obtain biotin labeled miRNA.
hyb_protocol: Array hybridization and wash were performed by GeneChip® Hybridization, Wash and Stain Kit (P/N900720, Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) and GeneChip Eukaryotic Hybridization Control Kit (P/N900454, Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) in Hybridization Oven 645 (P/N 00-0331 (220V), Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) and Fluidics Station 450 (P/N 00-0079, Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) according to the manufacturer’s instructions.
scan_protocol: Arrays were scanned by GeneChip® Scanner 7G (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) and Command Console Software 3.2 (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA, US) with default settings.
description.1: Gene expression after 24hr in ECs without melatonin treatment.
data_processing: The data were analyzed with Microarray Suite version 5.0 (MAS 5.0) using Affymetrix default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method. The trimmed mean target intensity of each array was arbitrarily set to 100.
contact_institute: fourth affiliated hospital of China Medical University
